(47, 'Airmatic Pump', 'seller', 111, 10, 25, '61', 0, '[\"uploads\\/products\\/photos\\/THGW2EgKPrRTgGwoj7JRzd5dZw0g10xfpsA2I9U9.jpeg\",\"uploads\\/products\\/photos\\/OZK3xnc73o4Hmdb6OSKtdx6vJHWNTQI1WvodJb9O.jpeg\"]', NULL, 'uploads/products/featured/lb7OW4HlqQyEmHgjIw8p4czfQM2EAlTdev2IXyyT.jpeg', NULL, NULL, NULL, '\"Airmatic Pump,Spare parts,Mercedes,Automobile\"', 'retail', '<ul><li>Air bag suspensions system uses a system of inflatable air bags filled with compressed air to suspend the vehicle off the ground. Air Compressors provide air to the integral components of your vehicle’s air ride suspension, keeping air springs and air shocks inflated to a necessary height based on your carrying load, towing and passengers. A properly working air suspension will keep your vehicle’s ride a smoother, more enjoyable one, and help with vehicle stability, braking and fuel economy.</li></ul>', 105000, 0, 0, 0, '[\"1\"]', '[{\"attribute_id\":\"1\",\"values\":[\"\"]}]', '[]', NULL, 0, 1, 0, 20, NULL, 0.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'flat_rate', 0.00, 0, 'Mercedes', 'Spare Parts', 'Airmatic Pump', NULL, NULL, 'airmatic-pump', 0.00, NULL, '2021-01-07 01:08:40', '2021-01-12 22:05:15', NULL, NULL, 0, 'Airmatic Pump GL 164<br><ul></ul>', 0.00),
