aries and this is why most applications require a “bouquet” of diodes – multiple diodes are carefully assembled to provide efficient and reliable light.In order to function, LED bulbs use DC electrical power One of the main benefits of these LED bulbs is that they can efficiently replaced the soft, conventional spot lights and minimize the energy consumption. The power ranges, but the average power of an LED bulb is of 3W (which replaces a conventional spot light of 50W).<br><u></u><br>', 0.00),
